    "originContent": "This project features the simulation of a custom vehicle with **Ackermann steering capabilities**, developed using **ROS2** and the **Gazebo Sim Harmonic environment**. The model integrates a variety of sensors and navigation tools for autonomous operation, making it one of the first implementations of an Ackermann steering vehicle in this simulation framework.",
